#####
# Xcode
#

[Bb]uild/ # slash on the end, so we only remove the FOLDER, not any files that were badly named "build"
*.pbxuser # http://lists.apple.com/archives/xcode-users/2004/Jan/msg00193.html
!default.pbxuser # whitelist the default, some projects need to use these
*.mode1v3 # http://lists.apple.com/archives/xcode-users/2007/Oct/msg00465.html
!default.mode1v3 # whitelist the default, some projects need to use these
*.mode2v3 # http://lists.apple.com/archives/xcode-users/2007/Oct/msg00465.html
!default.mode2v3 # whitelist the default, some projects need to use these
*.perspectivev3 # http://stackoverflow.com/questions/5223297/xcode-projects-what-is-a-perspectivev3-file
!default.perspectivev3 # whitelist the default, some projects need to use these
xcuserdata
*.xccheckout
*.moved-aside
DerivedData/ # slash on the end, so we only remove the FOLDER, not any files that were badly named "DerivedData"
*.hmap
*.ipa
*.xcuserstate
*~.nib # NIB/XIB files still exist even on Storyboard projects, so we want this...



